<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink148-kilavi">
        kaḷavoḻukkattiṉ viḷaivaṟiyātu añciya varuttanīṅka vatuvai karaṇavakaiyāṉ muṭittapiṉpu talaimakaṉaip paḷḷiyiṭattu uykkuntōḻi colliyatu.</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
          Spoken by the confidante who urged the hero into the bedroom having completed the marriage rites, so that the sorrow of having feared, not knowing the consequence of the secret relationship, abates.  </p>
 </div>     
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink148">
<l>ekkar ñāḻa likantupaṭu peruñciṉai</l>
<l>vīyiṉitu kamaḻun tuṟaivaṉai</l>
<l>nīyiṉitu muyaṅkumati kāta lōyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Oh lovely one! Will you pleasantly embrace the man from the ghat</l>
        <l> Where blossoms on big branches of Ñāḻal trees in the dunes have overgrown,</l>
        <l> Are pleasantly fragrant? </l>     </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
